HEADWORD: Bimedial
<hw>Bi*me"di*al</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>bi-</ets> + <ets>medial</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Geom.)</fld>
<def>Applied to a line which is the sum of two lines commensurable only
in power (as the side and diagonal of a square).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

